olitics%2Farticle%2F3022668%2Friot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHUw8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=613c013a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.scmp.com/news/hong-kong/politics/article/3022668/riot-police-protesters-clash-unprecedented-violence-hong</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Court 出左injunction ，聽日仲入去既，自己睇路，<br />\n林鄭就係想拎&ldquo;<ins>法庭授權警察清機場&rdquo;</ins></span></span>"},{"pid":"e1a9dd617554fed65ebcbbbcd0637460d855f8cc","tid":1468081,"uid":168492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T18:15:40.000Z","msg":"不割呀"}]}